title: Here’s what Naya Rivera named her baby boy
text:
Other Articles 'Talvar' box office collections: Irrfan Khan starrer records 25% occupancy rate on day 1 'Singh Is Bling' box office collections: Akshay Kumar starrer gathers 80% occupancy on day 1 'Girls Next Door' star Bridget Marquardt engaged to beau Nick Carpenter Following the announcement of Naya Rivera and Ryan Dorsey’s baby boy’s birth, his date of birth and name has been revealed.
According to sources, the ‘Glee’ actress welcomed her son, Josey Hollis Dorsey, on September 17, 2015, at Cedars-Sinai Hospital in Los Angeles, reports E! Online.
The 28-year-old actress announced her pregnancy in April by posting a photo of “bun in the oven” on social media.
First Published on October 01, 2015 5:30 pm
